UDV Gold Issime Eau de Parfum - 75 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.553

The Gold Issime resembles a drop of golden ambrosia packaged in a feminine form. Its captivating fragrance is a unique combination of aldehydic and floral fragrances that enchant with their union. Launched by the established French perfume house Ulric de Varens this luxury Eau de Parfum is designed for the essential woman in you with her passions emotions and vitality reflecting in her fashion choices. The perfume comes beautifully packaged in an elegant delicate flacon and delights with its form and spirit. A delicate aldehydic start raises its bar when it melts into a floral bouquet of notes comprising the sweet Ylang Rose Jasmine and Violet and embraces you with a flattering aura of pleasantness. With impressive longevity and prolonged sillage the Floral Aldehyde notes of this perfume exude a romantic charm that you simply cannot ignore.
